1
00:00:00,428 --> 00:00:08,528
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,703 --> 00:00:16,940
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,178 --> 00:00:19,169
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,183 --> 00:00:25,949
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,020 --> 00:00:29,387
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,590 --> 00:00:33,151
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,527 --> 00:00:36,894
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:36,964 --> 00:00:44,393
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,472 --> 00:00:53,608
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,681 --> 00:01:01,713
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,956 --> 00:01:08,794
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,863 --> 00:01:16,929
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,238 --> 00:01:25,703
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:27,805
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:37,369 --> 00:01:40,167
Where am I?!

16
00:01:46,578 --> 00:01:48,876
I've been saved.

17
00:01:49,748 --> 00:01:50,680
Oh?

18
00:01:51,316 --> 00:01:55,082
Awesome... He's pretty darn big...

19
00:01:56,354 --> 00:01:57,412
Oh yeah...

20
00:02:06,765 --> 00:02:13,967
This is a... frog... isn't it...?

21
00:02:18,910 --> 00:02:21,504
Oopsadaisy...

22
00:02:23,515 --> 00:02:24,812
Let's see now...

23
00:02:26,718 --> 00:02:28,583
No tail!

24
00:02:30,388 --> 00:02:32,481
This is...!

25
00:02:32,824 --> 00:02:34,348
Not like this one.

26
00:02:34,959 --> 00:02:36,586
Or that one.

27
00:02:36,961 --> 00:02:38,326
It's really...

28
00:02:38,396 --> 00:02:39,420
A real...

29
00:02:39,497 --> 00:02:41,124
Frog

30
00:02:42,233 --> 00:02:48,172
<i>He Flies! He Jumps! He Lurks!</i>
<i>Chief Toad Appears!</i>

31
00:02:49,941 --> 00:02:52,933
<i>Looks like he extracted the</i>
<i>Chakra of the Nine Tailed Fox</i>

32
00:02:53,011 --> 00:02:54,911
<i>all on his own this time.</i>

33
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:59,241
<i>But still, one certainly can't</i>
<i>say he's stable yet...</i>

34
00:02:59,484 --> 00:03:02,078
<i>He overused the large Charka...</i>

35
00:03:02,454 --> 00:03:06,356
<i>To think that of all the frogs</i>
<i>he summoned that one...</i>

36
00:03:09,027 --> 00:03:10,551
I did it...

37
00:03:10,628 --> 00:03:12,027
Hey, you little brat!

38
00:03:12,097 --> 00:03:12,791
Huh?

39
00:03:12,864 --> 00:03:14,661
Huh? Huh? Huh?!

40
00:03:20,839 --> 00:03:22,966
You little brat...

41
00:03:23,041 --> 00:03:26,499
On whose head do you think
you're raising a ruckus!

42
00:03:26,911 --> 00:03:32,975
This is the top of Gamabunta,
the Chief Toad's head! You idiot!

43
00:03:33,084 --> 00:03:35,052
Quiet down...

44
00:03:36,788 --> 00:03:37,652
Oh!

45
00:03:44,796 --> 00:03:47,390
W-What the heck is this guy?!

46
00:03:47,465 --> 00:03:49,160
He seems pretty awesome, but...

47
00:03:49,234 --> 00:03:50,633
Gimme a break!

48
00:03:50,702 --> 00:03:54,160
Just when I'm breathing the air of
the free world after a long time,

49
00:03:54,239 --> 00:03:57,538
some weird kid is raising
a ruckus on top of my head.

50
00:03:57,609 --> 00:04:01,841
Hey! Jiraiya! Where are you?!

51
00:04:02,113 --> 00:04:05,105
What the heck do
you think you're doing?!

52
00:04:06,684 --> 00:04:09,244
Hmm... This doesn't look good...

53
00:04:09,754 --> 00:04:13,713
'Cause even I can't handle
that Gamabunta...

54
00:04:13,992 --> 00:04:17,621
Jiraiya! Hurry up and
show yourself, you idiot!

55
00:04:18,696 --> 00:04:22,723
Hmmm... It would be troublesome if
that Gama found me out...

56
00:04:22,801 --> 00:04:24,962
I better get my ass out of here
without any further delay.

57
00:04:25,470 --> 00:04:27,768
Hey, little brat!

58
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:29,101
Y-Yes...?

59
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,504
Where's Jiraiya?

60
00:04:31,709 --> 00:04:33,370
Huh? Jiraiya?

61
00:04:33,678 --> 00:04:34,770
Who's that...?

62
00:04:34,846 --> 00:04:39,215
I'm talking about that lecher who
calls himself Toad Sage or something!

63
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:42,285
Where's Jiraiya? Huh?!

64
00:04:44,189 --> 00:04:45,781
<i>S-Scary...</i>

65
00:04:46,057 --> 00:04:48,890
If you just follow my orders,

66
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:51,520
I wouldn't mind making you
my henchman!

67
00:04:51,696 --> 00:04:54,290
Hurry up and answer me!

68
00:04:54,866 --> 00:04:56,925
Okay! If you're talking about
the Pervy Sage

69
00:04:57,001 --> 00:04:59,367
he's on the cliff up there,
Chief Toad.

70
00:04:59,704 --> 00:05:01,262
Up there, huh...?

71
00:05:01,673 --> 00:05:04,836
Um... Can I ask you one question?

72
00:05:05,009 --> 00:05:06,476
What is it?

73
00:05:07,612 --> 00:05:09,705
What business do you have
with that Pervy Sage?

74
00:05:09,848 --> 00:05:13,409
That's the question I want
to ask that pervert!

75
00:05:13,751 --> 00:05:19,383
What the heck does he want
summoning me to a place like this?!

76
00:05:20,358 --> 00:05:21,382
B-But...

77
00:05:21,459 --> 00:05:22,483
What is it?

78
00:05:23,728 --> 00:05:27,061
I'm the one who summoned
you, Chief Toad...

79
00:05:27,198 --> 00:05:28,392
I fell off the cliff...

80
00:05:28,466 --> 00:05:30,866
and thought maybe you
could come to my aid...

81
00:05:31,236 --> 00:05:32,396
Please...

82
00:05:33,371 --> 00:05:34,770
Hmm?

83
00:05:43,781 --> 00:05:47,717
What does a kid like you think
he's saying out of the blue.

84
00:05:48,753 --> 00:05:54,919
There's no way a little squirt like
you could summon a guy like me.

85
00:05:55,059 --> 00:05:58,790
It's... it's true...
I really truly summoned you...

86
00:05:58,863 --> 00:05:59,921
Believe it!

87
00:06:08,973 --> 00:06:10,668
You jerk frog!

88
00:06:10,942 --> 00:06:11,931
Huh?

89
00:06:12,010 --> 00:06:13,534
You've been condescending to me

90
00:06:13,611 --> 00:06:15,602
and saying whatever you
please since earlier on!

91
00:06:15,813 --> 00:06:21,843
Since I summoned you,
I'm your master!

92
00:06:22,086 --> 00:06:25,385
Huh? What was that?

93
00:06:25,557 --> 00:06:28,583
Hey, who do you think
you're talking to?!

94
00:06:28,793 --> 00:06:29,760
A little squirt like you,

95
00:06:29,827 --> 00:06:33,024
who isn't even able to exchange cups
of sake as a pledge of friendship,

96
00:06:33,097 --> 00:06:35,327
is saying to Lord Gamabunta,
that you're his master?

97
00:06:35,667 --> 00:06:39,262
I could kill you for that! Hey!

98
00:06:39,871 --> 00:06:40,599
Huh...

99
00:06:53,117 --> 00:06:55,210
Oohhh...

100
00:07:13,171 --> 00:07:16,197
It looks like he emerged on top,
that Gamabunta...

101
00:07:22,947 --> 00:07:25,177
Awesome...

102
00:07:29,621 --> 00:07:31,919
I hate to tell you this, little brat,

103
00:07:31,990 --> 00:07:34,322
but even if I were to concede
a hundred steps to you...

104
00:07:34,392 --> 00:07:35,359
No, concede a thousand steps to you,

105
00:07:35,426 --> 00:07:39,157
and even if it really was true that
it was you who summoned me...

106
00:07:39,230 --> 00:07:42,427
If you're the kind of guy who
falls off my back that easily,

107
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:46,334
there's no way I could
admit you as my master...

108
00:07:46,404 --> 00:07:48,065
Huh?! Huh?!

109
00:07:49,474 --> 00:07:52,966
Now then... I'm here in the
free world after a long time...

110
00:07:53,044 --> 00:07:55,410
If Jiraiya doesn't have
any business with me,

111
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:58,347
I think I'll kick back for a while.

112
00:07:58,850 --> 00:08:00,340
Hey! Wait!

113
00:08:00,652 --> 00:08:03,780
Why don't you just go home
and sleep or something?

114
00:08:04,022 --> 00:08:07,788
'Cause it looks like you're incapable
of serving even as my henchman.

115
00:08:14,065 --> 00:08:15,555
Darn it!

116
00:08:26,611 --> 00:08:29,136
W-What the heck do you think
you're doing, you little brat?

117
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:31,548
If my making you recognize that
I summoned you

118
00:08:31,616 --> 00:08:33,607
depends on my not falling
off your back, then...!

119
00:08:33,685 --> 00:08:38,850
Then I won't get off your back
the entire day today no matter what!

120
00:08:39,123 --> 00:08:40,317
What?!

121
00:08:40,725 --> 00:08:45,992
And by my doing that I'll make
you recognize me as your master!

122
00:08:46,464 --> 00:08:51,766
You little brat! Don't get all carried away
thinking I'll go easy on you!

123
00:08:52,503 --> 00:08:53,128
Huh?!

124
00:08:53,671 --> 00:08:55,901
Fall!

125
00:09:01,813 --> 00:09:03,246
Chakra adhesion!

126
00:09:05,917 --> 00:09:07,976
There's not enough Chakra!

127
00:09:09,053 --> 00:09:11,920
Listen carefully, Chief Toad!

128
00:09:11,989 --> 00:09:14,583
My name is Naruto Uzumaki!

129
00:09:14,659 --> 00:09:17,492
I'm a man who will become Hokage
in the future. Don't forget that!

130
00:09:17,562 --> 00:09:19,496
Who cares!

131
00:09:25,737 --> 00:09:29,229
This is getting pretty interesting.

132
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,498
Hey!

133
00:09:32,243 --> 00:09:33,039
Oh my gosh!

134
00:09:36,781 --> 00:09:41,844
Sorry Naruto,
but I've gotta get back to work!

135
00:09:43,387 --> 00:09:45,787
Research... research...

136
00:09:55,133 --> 00:09:56,566
Bust off!

137
00:10:13,684 --> 00:10:15,015
Welcome!

138
00:10:15,086 --> 00:10:16,610
I'm gonna eat my fill.

139
00:10:17,421 --> 00:10:20,720
Huh... Those guys are
eathing barbecue again, huh?

140
00:10:21,092 --> 00:10:24,061
A reward for having trained
earnestly... maybe?

141
00:10:24,462 --> 00:10:28,626
I thought you were told not to
let Gaara out of your sight...

142
00:10:28,933 --> 00:10:31,663
Don't worry...
even somebody like him...

143
00:10:32,403 --> 00:10:35,338
wouldn't dare to do anything
in broad daylight.

144
00:10:36,274 --> 00:10:39,300
More importantly,
that guy Shikamaru or whatever,

145
00:10:39,377 --> 00:10:41,675
he's the first guy
you're fighting, right?

146
00:10:42,079 --> 00:10:44,411
Shouldn't you be formulating
a battle plan?

147
00:10:44,949 --> 00:10:48,908
Humph... There's no way I would
lose to a guy of that level...

148
00:10:49,187 --> 00:10:50,176
Besides...

149
00:10:50,254 --> 00:10:51,482
You botched it, didn't you?

150
00:10:51,556 --> 00:10:52,181
Huh?

151
00:10:52,657 --> 00:10:55,626
If you had taken the exam
one year earlier,

152
00:10:55,693 --> 00:10:58,161
you would have made
the Chunin easily...

153
00:10:59,697 --> 00:11:00,595
Don't say it...

154
00:11:06,404 --> 00:11:07,894
What was that?!

155
00:11:08,372 --> 00:11:10,397
The upcoming Chunin Exam...

156
00:11:10,741 --> 00:11:14,734
I'll have the three of you from
our Sand Village take the exam...

157
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:19,079
But the reason for doing that
is not to pass the Chunin Exam!

158
00:11:20,017 --> 00:11:22,212
It is to use the opportunity
of the Chunin Exam...

159
00:11:22,286 --> 00:11:24,811
to crush Leaf Village!

160
00:11:25,289 --> 00:11:31,057
But why? Don't we have
a treaty with Leaf Village?!

161
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:35,699
That treaty is the problem.

162
00:11:35,833 --> 00:11:36,390
Oh.

163
00:11:36,567 --> 00:11:37,625
What do you mean?

164
00:11:38,736 --> 00:11:41,762
You Genin are not aware of
the detail but...

165
00:11:42,073 --> 00:11:44,007
At the time the treaty was concluded,

166
00:11:44,275 --> 00:11:48,405
that idiot feudal lord of Land of Wind
not only aggressively scaled down

167
00:11:48,479 --> 00:11:51,676
the arsenal of
the Hidden Sand Village...

168
00:11:52,083 --> 00:11:53,607
he delegated to the Leaf Village

169
00:11:53,684 --> 00:11:56,244
matters that should have been handled
by our country, and moreover,

170
00:11:56,320 --> 00:12:02,486
significantly cut our country's budget
and slashed the number of Shinobi.

171
00:12:02,927 --> 00:12:04,622
When we have an idiot leader,

172
00:12:04,695 --> 00:12:07,186
we, the arms and legs
of the country, suffer.

173
00:12:07,265 --> 00:12:09,756
The only choice we had left
was to improve the quality

174
00:12:09,834 --> 00:12:13,600
of each and every Shinobi in order
to maintain our country's military power...

175
00:12:14,338 --> 00:12:18,604
That's why Shinobi like
you were created...

176
00:12:19,543 --> 00:12:21,067
Gaara...

177
00:12:21,979 --> 00:12:26,916
The Land of Wind's security is
in extreme danger right now!

178
00:12:27,985 --> 00:12:32,012
But the aides
of that idiot feudal lord...

179
00:12:32,089 --> 00:12:34,057
don't have a clue!

180
00:12:35,226 --> 00:12:36,386
Lord Kazekage

181
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:40,556
who detected the weakening in the military
strength of the Hidden Sand Village,

182
00:12:40,798 --> 00:12:42,891
joined hands with
the Hidden Sound Village

183
00:12:42,967 --> 00:12:45,731
and decided to take down
the Hidden Leaf Village...

184
00:12:46,437 --> 00:12:49,372
In addition to restoring Sand
Village authority...

185
00:12:49,507 --> 00:12:51,941
this needs to be done in order
to make that idiot feudal lord

186
00:12:52,009 --> 00:12:54,500
aware of the importance of
crisis preparedness...

187
00:12:57,949 --> 00:13:01,009
If any more time passes,
our Sand Village will totally lose

188
00:13:01,085 --> 00:13:04,350
its military capabilities
against the Leaf Village...

189
00:13:05,056 --> 00:13:06,523
Now is the only chance...

190
00:13:07,391 --> 00:13:12,385
The success of that mission...
Gaara... depends on your work...

191
00:13:14,999 --> 00:13:16,159
Yeah...

192
00:13:17,268 --> 00:13:19,133
If the strategy is carried out,

193
00:13:19,203 --> 00:13:21,262
it will certainly lead to war
with the Leaf Village.

194
00:13:22,073 --> 00:13:24,564
We'll be at war again...?

195
00:13:25,543 --> 00:13:29,070
The cost to human life in implementing
the treaty was very great...

196
00:13:29,146 --> 00:13:34,174
and if it is broken... then again...
many people will die...

197
00:13:34,385 --> 00:13:36,182
H-Hey... Temari...

198
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:39,683
This is the will of Lord Kazekage.

199
00:13:40,858 --> 00:13:42,348
Of Lord Kazekage?

200
00:13:43,094 --> 00:13:45,722
After all, Shinobi are simply
tools for fighting

201
00:13:45,997 --> 00:13:52,835
The treaty did nothing more than
jeopardize our very existence.

202
00:13:55,306 --> 00:13:57,501
This is a super A rank mission.

203
00:13:57,908 --> 00:13:59,739
See it through with great care!

204
00:14:00,411 --> 00:14:01,173
Okay.

205
00:14:02,413 --> 00:14:03,311
Yes...

206
00:14:07,184 --> 00:14:11,644
A day sure is long when
one's not doing anything.

207
00:14:13,257 --> 00:14:14,417
I guess...

208
00:14:38,182 --> 00:14:41,242
<i>Darn... What an obstinate little squirt.</i>

209
00:15:02,907 --> 00:15:08,368
Goodness... that Naruto seems
like he's in agony...

210
00:15:10,514 --> 00:15:13,347
He must have exhausted
most of his Chakra

211
00:15:13,417 --> 00:15:16,682
when he summoned Gamabunta...

212
00:15:17,588 --> 00:15:19,021
Look, look, isn't that pretty...

213
00:15:19,090 --> 00:15:20,114
The rainbow...

214
00:15:20,191 --> 00:15:21,123
Gorgeous...

215
00:15:22,126 --> 00:15:25,254
Yeah, yeah, absolutely gorgeous, isn't it.

216
00:15:33,337 --> 00:15:36,101
Good work, Baki.

217
00:15:36,740 --> 00:15:40,767
Lord Kazekage, I successfully
moved all three pawns

218
00:15:40,845 --> 00:15:43,075
to the real battle as planned.

219
00:15:44,782 --> 00:15:48,115
The agreement with the Sound Village side
has been progressing with no problem too.

220
00:15:48,185 --> 00:15:48,879
Yes, sir.

221
00:15:51,489 --> 00:15:52,547
This is...

222
00:15:53,124 --> 00:15:55,991
A decisive action plan from
the Sound Village

223
00:16:11,342 --> 00:16:13,173
You still have something you want?

224
00:16:13,644 --> 00:16:14,542
Well...

225
00:16:14,778 --> 00:16:16,973
What is it? Come out with it.

226
00:16:17,047 --> 00:16:20,483
Yes, sir... I was wondering if you
could position some soldiers

227
00:16:20,551 --> 00:16:22,917
near the border on the pretext of
undertaking a tactical exercise.

228
00:16:23,154 --> 00:16:24,382
With only the four of us...

229
00:16:24,989 --> 00:16:26,923
The Leaf Village aren't idiots either.

230
00:16:27,525 --> 00:16:29,925
Their Anbu black ops
are moving about.

231
00:16:30,194 --> 00:16:33,960
If we do that, they will see right through
what we're contemplating.

232
00:16:34,031 --> 00:16:36,431
But with only our current
military capability...

233
00:16:36,967 --> 00:16:39,492
That's why I sent Gaara and
the others out there.

234
00:16:40,204 --> 00:16:45,699
The restoration of the authority of
the Hidden Sand Village is resting on you.

235
00:16:47,244 --> 00:16:49,405
Well... Go.

236
00:16:49,647 --> 00:16:50,136
Yes, sir.

237
00:16:59,823 --> 00:17:04,192
There's only a little more time remaining
until the sun sets completely...

238
00:17:04,261 --> 00:17:05,489
and if I don't fall off...

239
00:17:05,563 --> 00:17:07,997
I'll be the master!

240
00:17:08,666 --> 00:17:09,860
What's that to me?!

241
00:17:09,934 --> 00:17:12,596
You came up with this
whole thing unilaterally.

242
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:15,230
I'm not falling off, no matter what!

243
00:17:17,274 --> 00:17:21,176
<i>That Naruto...</i>
<i>he's already way past his limit...</i>

244
00:17:21,912 --> 00:17:24,972
<i>I wouldn't be surprised if</i>
<i>he fell off any minute now...</i>

245
00:17:30,154 --> 00:17:33,920
<i>I could simply ignore what</i>
<i>a brat like him says...</i>

246
00:17:33,991 --> 00:17:38,951
<i>but taking a lick really irritates me.</i>

247
00:17:39,263 --> 00:17:42,426
<i>I'm gonna bring this</i>
<i>to an end once and for all...</i>

248
00:17:43,167 --> 00:17:46,136
Hey, brat... what's your name?

249
00:17:46,470 --> 00:17:47,494
Naruto!

250
00:17:47,705 --> 00:17:49,468
It's Naruto Uzumaki!

251
00:17:49,974 --> 00:17:54,707
Naruto Uzumaki... Naruto!

252
00:17:54,778 --> 00:17:57,645
Don't hold it against me if you die!

253
00:18:07,391 --> 00:18:08,483
Oh...

254
00:18:08,759 --> 00:18:10,351
That Gamabunta!

255
00:18:10,427 --> 00:18:12,952
Now it's a matter of pride for him, too!

256
00:18:13,530 --> 00:18:14,326
Huh?!

257
00:18:15,399 --> 00:18:16,491
