I'm so close to succeeding!

260
00:18:33,884 --> 00:18:34,714
Hey!

261
00:18:34,785 --> 00:18:35,479
Oh...

262
00:18:35,552 --> 00:18:36,746
What?!

263
00:18:36,954 --> 00:18:37,978
That Naruto...

264
00:18:38,455 --> 00:18:41,652
He's squeezing out yet more Chakra
from that condition he's in.

265
00:18:54,204 --> 00:18:56,399
I'm falling...

266
00:19:17,761 --> 00:19:22,755
How do you like that, Gamabunta?
I'm still on your back!

267
00:19:24,335 --> 00:19:25,802
It's my victory!

268
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,870
Oh no! If he falls like that he'll die!

269
00:19:47,224 --> 00:19:52,457
<i>Too bad for you... You almost made it.</i>

270
00:19:56,367 --> 00:20:00,861
<i>To think that he could hold out like that</i>
<i>against a tough opponent like Gamabunta...</i>

271
00:20:16,487 --> 00:20:17,419
<i>Hm?!</i>

272
00:20:20,391 --> 00:20:24,725
<i>That, Jiraiya, meddling in...</i>

273
00:20:24,995 --> 00:20:26,826
<i>I am fully aware of the fact that...</i>

274
00:20:26,897 --> 00:20:29,923
<i>this guy here summoned</i>
<i>me all on his own.</i>

275
00:20:30,367 --> 00:20:33,734
<i>I mean, it's the first time since</i>
<i>the Fourth Hokage</i>

276
00:20:33,804 --> 00:20:36,398
<i>that somebody climbed on my head.</i>

277
00:20:36,807 --> 00:20:39,833
<i>As might be expected,</i>
<i>he must be totally drained.</i>

278
00:20:40,010 --> 00:20:43,912
<i>I don't mind dispensing some</i>
<i>of my power to him but...</i>

279
00:20:44,314 --> 00:20:48,307
<i>Taking him to that place would be best.</i>

280
00:20:51,922 --> 00:20:53,184
